----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party dependencies
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project depends on the following crates whose licenses impose
obligations beyond Apache-2.0/MIT. Users distributing binaries that
incorporate this code should review them.

  horned-owl  (LGPL-3.0)
      https://github.com/phillord/horned-owl
      Used as our OWL model and parser. The LGPL-3.0 permits use under
      Apache-2.0/MIT projects, but distributors of binaries must allow
      end-users to relink against modified versions of horned-owl. In
      practice this is satisfied by providing access to the unmodified
      source of horned-owl and the object files of rustdl, which is
      automatic for open-source distributions via cargo and GitHub.

A full per-dependency license inventory is generated by `cargo deny list`
or `cargo about generate`. Run `cargo xtask third-party-licenses` to
refresh this NOTICE.
